MapLinks.Description: Instructors at the Avery J. Johnson Academy of Military Science ensure their Spartans are prepared for any challenge.
Power still courses through the walls of this neglected Axys facility.
Buried for millennia, this ancient structure rises from beneath the sands.
Sabre proving grounds test the limits of human velocity.
These beacons are no stranger to explosive conflict.
UNSC forces have yet to breach this Banished encampment.
The tranquility of this Mombasa back alley is pierced by the sound of heavy gunfire.
Aquarius Terraforming Solutions: Industry leader in returning life to barren worlds.
Spent shells rain like water in this ancient sanctuary.
